    "rationale": "This Minimal-profile package documents the credibility assessment outcome. Per the governing project requirements specification, all 13 credibility factors have been evaluated against MRL 5 thresholds. Seven factors were formally assessed; all achieved levels fall below required levels. Six factors were flagged as not-assessed epistemic gaps. The structured bindsRequirement linkage is intentionally absent from this Minimal-profile submission; project requirements are referenced in prose only. The overall credibility determination is recorded as Accepted for package submission purposes pending resolution of all factor gaps.",
